To run the Application-

-- Prerequisites
 1) Maven
 2) JAVA

-- Database
 1) H2 (In-memory database)

-- To Run
 1) mvn spring-boot:run

-- To Run on Docker
 1) mvn clean package (generate jar file)
 2) docker build -t myapp .
 3) docker run -p 8080:8080 myapp

-- For API documentation Swagger is used. To access documentation use "http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html#/main-controller"

-- Description
 This is a simple task management tool. The tool will allow an end user to create, manage and delete tasks using a web interface.